  "title" : "What is Eclipse&#39;s Ctrl+O (Show Outline) shortcut equivalent in IntelliJ IDEA?",
  "body" : "<p>I like to use Eclipse's shortcut <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>O</kbd> which outlines the current source. Is there an equivalent shortcut in IntelliJ IDEA?</p>\n\n<p>It opens a dialog which allows for quick search of methods and fields in a class.</p>\n"
